high_descs: Turn to your right and face the island
Pick up the knife on the island
Turn to your left then walk straight turn to your left face the counter beside the stove
Put the knife in the mug on the counter
Pick up the mug with knife on the counter
Turn to your right then head to the sink on your left
Put the mug with knife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife in the sink

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the knife in the gray coffee mug.
Pick up the coffee mug.
Turn right and walk along the counter to the sink.
Place the mug in the sink in front of and to the left of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a knife in it in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and move to the brown counter to the right of the oven.
Pick up the large knife off of the counter.
Turn around and head to the counter that is by the toaster.
Place the knife inside the white mug that is near the toaster.
Pick up the mug with the knife off the counter.
Turn around and move to the sink across the room.
Place the white mug and knife into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Gather white mug with knife it in to be placed in the sink.
